{"text_id":105681,"tokens":["If"," you","'","ve"," been"," diagnosed"," with"," a"," leaking"," heart"," valve",","," you"," may"," need"," treatment"," to"," prevent"," further"," damage"," to"," your"," heart","."," The"," type"," of"," treatment"," will"," depend"," on"," the"," kind"," of"," valve"," leak"," that"," you"," have","."," The"," treatment"," of"," a"," leaky"," heart"," valve"," also"," depends"," upon"," the"," severity"," of"," disease","."," Here"," are"," some"," ways"," to"," treat"," a"," leaking"," heart"," valve",":","\n","1","."," Understand"," that"," the"," type"," of"," treatment"," will"," depend"," on"," the"," kind"," of"," valve"," leak"," that"," you"," have",".","\n","There"," are"," four"," types"," of"," heart"," valve"," problems",":"," stenosis"," (","narrow","ing","),"," pro","lapse"," (","bill","owing","),"," regurg","itation"," (","back","flow","),"," and"," atre","sia"," (","closed"," valve",")."," The"," type"," of"," treatment"," you"," will"," need"," depends"," on"," which"," type"," of"," valve"," leak"," you"," have",".","\n","2","."," Get"," a"," prescription"," for"," Dig","oxin"," (","Lan","oxin",").","\n","Dig","oxin"," helps"," to"," control"," your"," heart"," rate"," and"," increase"," your"," heart","'","s"," pumping"," capacity","."," This"," medication"," is"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," atrial"," fibrillation"," (","a"," type"," of"," irregular"," heartbeat",").","\n","3","."," Talk"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," different"," anticoag","ulants",".","\n","An","tico","ag","ulants",","," such"," as"," war","farin"," (","Cou","mad","in","),"," help"," to"," prevent"," blood"," clots"," from"," forming","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," atrial"," fibrillation"," or"," a"," history"," of"," blood"," clots",".","\n","4","."," Lower"," your"," cholesterol"," with"," stat","ins",".","\n","Stat","ins"," help"," to"," lower"," your"," cholesterol"," levels",","," which"," can"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," high"," cholesterol"," levels",".","\n","5","."," Take"," ang","iotensin"," II"," receptor"," blockers"," (","AR","Bs",").","\n","AR","Bs"," help"," to"," lower"," blood"," pressure"," and"," reduce"," the"," workload"," on"," the"," heart","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," high"," blood"," pressure",".","\n","6","."," Try"," taking"," ACE"," inhibitors",".","\n","ACE"," inhibitors"," also"," help"," to"," lower"," blood"," pressure"," and"," reduce"," the"," workload"," on"," the"," heart","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," heart"," failure",".","\n","7","."," Talk"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," beta","-","block","ers",".","\n","Beta","-","block","ers"," help"," to"," slow"," down"," the"," heart"," rate"," and"," reduce"," the"," workload"," on"," the"," heart","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," heart"," failure"," or"," atrial"," fibrillation",".","\n","8","."," Take"," diure","tics",".","\n","Di","ure","tics"," help"," to"," reduce"," excess"," fluid"," in"," the"," body",","," which"," can"," reduce"," the"," workload"," on"," the"," heart","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," heart"," failure",".","\n","9","."," Try"," taking"," anti","-","arr","hyth","mic"," medications",".","\n","Anti","-","arr","hyth","mic"," medications"," help"," to"," control"," irregular"," heart","beats"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," blood"," clots","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," atrial"," fibrillation",".","\n","1","0","."," Talk"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," different"," vas","odil","ators",".","\n","Vas","odil","ators"," help"," to"," dil","ate"," (","w","iden",")"," blood"," vessels"," and"," reduce"," the"," workload"," on"," the"," heart","."," These"," medications"," are"," often"," used"," in"," patients"," with"," heart"," failure"," or"," high"," blood"," pressure",".","\n","1","1","."," Understand"," that"," the"," type"," of"," surgery"," will"," depend"," on"," the"," type"," of"," heart"," valve"," leak",".","\n","If"," your"," valve"," leak"," is"," severe",","," surgery"," may"," be"," necessary"," to"," repair"," or"," replace"," the"," damaged"," valve","."," The"," type"," of"," surgery"," you"," will"," need"," depends"," on"," which"," type"," of"," valve"," leak"," you"," have",".","\n","1","2","."," Get"," surgery"," to"," repair"," your"," heart"," valves",".","\n","Valve"," repair"," surgery"," is"," often"," done"," for"," patients"," with"," mitral"," valve"," pro","lapse"," or"," tric","us","pid"," valve"," pro","lapse","."," During"," this"," surgery",","," the"," damaged"," or"," torn"," valve"," is"," repaired"," with"," synthetic"," patches"," or"," tissue",".","\n","1","3","."," Have"," your"," heart"," valves"," completely"," replaced",".","\n","Valve"," replacement"," surgery"," is"," often"," done"," for"," patients"," with"," severe"," valve"," stenosis"," or"," regurg","itation","."," During"," this"," surgery",","," the"," damaged"," valve"," is"," replaced"," with"," a"," mechanical"," valve"," or"," a"," tissue"," valve",".","\n","1","4","."," Get"," balloon"," val","v","ulo","p","lasty"," done",".","\n","Balloon"," val","v","ulo","p","lasty"," is"," a"," minimally"," invasive"," procedure"," that"," is"," often"," used"," for"," patients"," with"," aortic"," valve"," stenosis","."," During"," this"," procedure",","," a"," balloon"," catheter"," is"," inserted"," into"," the"," valve"," and"," inflated"," to"," widen"," the"," valve"," opening",".","\n","1","5","."," Quit"," smoking",".","\n","Smoking"," can"," increase"," the"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease"," and"," damage"," the"," heart"," valves","."," Quit","ting"," smoking"," can"," improve"," your"," heart"," health"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," further"," valve"," damage",".","\n","1","6","."," Eat"," a"," low","-","fat"," diet",".","\n","A"," diet"," high"," in"," saturated"," and"," trans"," fats"," can"," increase"," cholesterol"," levels"," and"," increase"," the"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease","."," Eating"," a"," low","-","fat"," diet"," can"," improve"," your"," heart"," health"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," further"," valve"," damage",".","\n","1","7","."," Exercise"," regularly",".","\n","Regular"," exercise"," can"," improve"," heart"," health"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease","."," Talk"," to"," your"," doctor"," about"," an"," exercise"," plan"," that"," is"," safe"," for"," you",".","\n","1","8","."," Take"," care"," of"," your"," teeth"," and"," gums",".","\n","Poor"," oral"," health"," has"," been"," linked"," to"," an"," increased"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease","."," Brush"," and"," floss"," regularly"," and"," see"," your"," dentist"," for"," regular"," check","ups",".","\n","1","9","."," Give"," your"," doctor"," your"," full"," medical"," history",".","\n","Your"," medical"," history"," can"," help"," your"," doctor"," determine"," the"," best"," treatment"," for"," your"," valve"," leak","."," Be"," sure"," to"," provide"," your"," doctor"," with"," a"," complete"," medical"," history",","," including"," any"," medications"," you"," are"," currently"," taking",".","\n","2","0","."," Get"," an"," echocardio","gram"," done",".","\n","An"," echocardio","gram"," is"," an"," imaging"," test"," that"," can"," help"," diagnose"," a"," valve"," leak"," and"," determine"," the"," severity"," of"," the"," leak",".","\n","2","1","."," Set"," up"," an"," appointment"," for"," an"," electrocardio","gram",".","\n","An"," electrocardio","gram"," (","ECG",")"," measures"," the"," electrical"," activity"," of"," the"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt